			purpose = <"To record a Cobb angle.">
			use = <"Use to record a Cobb angle.
            
            This archetype is designed to be nested within the 'Findings' SLOT in the Node.imaging_exam_spine, Node.imaging_exam-cervical_spine, Node.imaging_exam-thoracic_spine, Node.imaging_exam-lumbal_spine, the 'Structured imaging findings' SLOT in the OBSERVATION.imaging_exam_result or within other relevant Node.imaging_exam archetypes, but can also be used within other ENTRY or Node archetypes, where clinically appropriate. 
            
            Details about start and end points of the measurement, body postion, supporting devices or method used to measure the angle is to be recorded in OBSERVATION.imaging_exam or in other relevant ENTRY archetypes.">
